  <h3>Stay healthy with lifestyle changes</h3>




<div class="block_column">
  <p>Finding healthy outlets for bipolar disorder is important. Relaxation techniques, self-care and exercise can enhance your treatment and keep you on a healthier path.
  
    <br/>
    
      <span class="arrow_right"><a href="/conditions/mental-behavioral-health/bipolar-disorder/living-with-bipolar-disorder/balancing-daily-life" >Find out more</a></span>
    
  
  </p>
  
</div>



